{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-16","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovom delu razgovora, Sara predlaže igranje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Gartic</span> na nadolazećoj večeri igara. Koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">maybe</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we can</span> da pokaže mogućnost da se ovo dogodi.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Maybe</span> je reč koja se koristi kada predlažeš mogućnost, ali ne znaš da li ta mogućnost može ili ne može da se ostvari. Ukazuje na to da nisi napravio čvrst plan, ali da si otvoren za tu ideju. Na primer: ako te neko pita da li želiš da odeš u bioskop, možeš reći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Maybe</span> ako ne znaš da li želiš da odeš ili da si slobodan.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We can</span> Koristi se za predlaganje ideje ili podnošenje predloga na uštasan način. Pokazuje da osobe u razgovoru imaju mogućnost ili opciju da nešto urade. Primer: ako želiš da predložiš igranje igre, možeš reći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">We can play a game</span> dati tu ideju.</p>\n<p>Razlika između <span class=\"highlighted-text\">maybe</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we can</span> je u tome što <span class=\"highlighted-text\">maybe</span> predlaže mogućnost bez organizovanja formalnog plana, dok <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we can</span> predlaže ideju ili predlog na umeren način.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-16"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Sarah šta znači kada se kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Maybe we can...</span>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Nije dozvoljeno igrati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Gartic</span>.</p>","feedback":"<p>Predlog Sare nije obavezan.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Sigurno će igrati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Gartic</span> drugog puta.</p>","feedback":"<p>Predlog Sare nije stabilan plan.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Nije moguće uopšte igrati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Gartic</span>.</p>","feedback":"<p>Predlog Sare nije uslov.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Postoji mogućnost igranja <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Gartic</span> narednih dana.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"1.3-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":35.3,"finishTimestamp":39.54},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":5.24,"dialogue":{"text":"Oh, yeah! 'Gartic' is another favorite. Maybe we can play 'Gartic' on the next game night?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":5.74,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 16","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","dashedName":"task-16","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":